data.name: lblMainStationSetup.Text
data.value:
Hi! It's your first time you use Waveface Stream Windows.
This computer will be setup as your Station. All the photos you uploaded from Stream apps will be send to this computer: {0} automatically through the Waveface Cloud.
Now please click on "OK" to enter your Stream. You can enter "Account Info" in the main program for further options.

data.name: lblSecondStationSetup.Text
data.value:
Hi! Thank you for using Waveface Stream Windows.
This computer will be setup as a part of your Waveface personal cloud, and enhance the performance of this computer and nearby devices. All the photos you uploaded from Stream apps will still be sent to your Station: {0} through the Waveface Cloud.
Now please click on "OK" to enter your Stream. You can enter "Account Info" in the main program for further options.
